664
01:16:43,600 --> 01:16:46,477
Then I'll put it in some food.

665
01:16:46,894 --> 01:16:49,022
This is my sister Julie.

666
01:16:49,355 --> 01:16:52,859
This is Ondrej. He's a doctor.

667
01:16:53,526 --> 01:16:57,113
I don't have to introduce you.
This is Jakub, a great musician.

668
01:16:57,113 --> 01:16:59,991
- Hi, I'm Jakub.
