Isn't cake more for weddings?

672
01:17:12,170 --> 01:17:15,131
Do you have any mixes?

673
01:17:15,882 --> 01:17:17,759
We must.

674
01:17:19,218 --> 01:17:22,055
I want to bake something.

675
01:17:25,975 --> 01:17:30,355
Ondrej, I don't know how
to get through to you.

676
01:17:38,655 --> 01:17:44,744
Look. You've made a mess
