702
01:20:44,423 --> 01:20:47,176
So I was looking at you
instead of at him.

703
01:20:48,761 --> 01:20:50,096
Whatever.

704
01:20:50,304 --> 01:20:54,350
- What did you bake?
- Some excellent pastry.

705
01:20:56,811 --> 01:21:00,147
I don't want any pastry.
I just want to sit down.

706
01:21:02,108 --> 01:21:03,359
Some party.

707
01:21:04,735 --> 01:21:09,282
- I'd like something to drink.
- We have some excellent pastry.

708
01:23:55,906 --> 01:23:58,617
